1. Write ChangeLog entry.

2. make dist, check that it builds and installs correctly.

3. git commit

4. git tag -s Release_X.Y.Z

5. Sign (gpg -b) and upload dist tarball 
   (sftp larsl@dl.sv.nongnu.org:/releases/ll-plugins).

6. Generate new API documentation, upload it, update the redirect page.

7. Update webpages.

8. Announce on http://freshmeat.net and any relevant mailing lists.
